{"tid":539052,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有關電腦掃描與顯影劑問題","createTime":"2018-01-24T08:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T07:02:07.000Z","uid":101237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c61c7d392d6e354431eeda35fc7cddcd38434c01","tid":539052,"uid":101237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"想請問如果舊年12月中做完電腦掃描，無落顯影劑；12月尾有落顯影劑做電影掃描；<br />\n<br />\n然後3月中唔會落顯影劑做多次掃描；5月中會落顯影劑做掃描<br />\n<br />\n呢個檢查密度的輻射，會唔會對身體有影響？<br />\n另外，相隔5個月再落顯影劑，對身體又會唔會有負作用？<br />\n<br />\n感謝巴絲打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155ed74ef036a76b16789a74de3f96ceaf353572","tid":539052,"uid":101237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69a57f98db75236898f1a304548e733afde4224","tid":539052,"uid":132677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:00:49.000Z","msg":"飲多d水 顯影劑會屙番出來 所以冇乜大影響"},{"pid":"49e958671e74c063df243342007e542de14d9dfe","tid":539052,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"輻射唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n顯影劑好似冇乜問題<br />\n個問題係有極少人會敏感, 導致生命危險, 所以要簽紙<br />\n你已經試過即係冇敏感, 再落都應該冇事"},{"pid":"8150e3a6472b8ea67dc1128763aaf5fd3a776b63","tid":539052,"uid":51021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e958671e74c063df243342007e542de14d9dfe","tid":539052,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"輻射唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n顯影劑好似冇乜問題<br />\n個問題係有極少人會敏感, 導致生命危險, 所以要簽紙<br />\n你已經試過即係冇敏感, 再落都應該冇事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:16:43.000Z","msg":"顯影劑應該係radioactive <br />\n不過應該劑量好細 坐小幾次飛機都係返度"},{"pid":"72e6bb165ab93e1f51ec2d0d217083d4698bca5e","tid":539052,"uid":28354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8150e3a6472b8ea67dc1128763aaf5fd3a776b63","tid":539052,"uid":51021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e958671e74c063df243342007e542de14d9dfe","tid":539052,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"輻射唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n顯影劑好似冇乜問題<br />\n個問題係有極少人會敏感, 導致生命危險, 所以要簽紙<br />\n你已經試過即係冇敏感, 再落都應該冇事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:16:43.000Z","msg":"顯影劑應該係radioactive <br />\n不過應該劑量好細 坐小幾次飛機都係返度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:19:09.000Z","msg":"同埋照咁睇應該4 5個月會decay曬"},{"pid":"d9c26554ecf684de887a15982464529189be15ff","tid":539052,"uid":67649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"CT 顯影劑唔係 radioactive 的。<br />\n<br />\nFrom US FDA<br />\n「A CT examination with an effective dose of 10 millisieverts (abbreviated mSv; 1 mSv = 1 mGy in the case of x-rays.) may be associated with an increase in the possibility of fatal cancer of approximately 1 chance in 2000. This increase in the possibility of a fatal cancer from radiation can be compared to the natural incidence of fatal cancer in the U.S. population, about 1 chance in 5 (equal to 400 chances in 2000). In other words, for any one person the risk of radiation-induced cancer is much smaller than the natural risk of cancer. If you combine the natural risk of a fatal cancer and the estimated risk from a 10 mSv CT scan, <span style=\"color: red;\">the total risk may increase from 400 chances in 2000 to 401 chances in 2000.</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fda.gov/Radiation-EmittingProducts/RadiationEmittingProductsandProcedures/MedicalImaging/MedicalX-Rays/ucm115329.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2FRadiation-EmittingProducts%2FRadiationEmittingProductsandProcedures%2FMedicalImaging%2FMedicalX-Rays%2Fucm115329.htm&d=ORNTrwOGgTfFwb0C8nnRxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6c5314f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fda.gov/Radiation-EmittingProducts/RadiationEmittingProductsandProcedures/MedicalImaging/MedicalX-Rays/ucm115329.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然照CT 係有輻射，不過劑量好少，會導致癌症嘅機會好低，<br />\n同埋醫生order 得嘅應該有佢嘅需要，所以唔洗擔心"},{"pid":"1549a6c6e022feb62c90d9ae29f9b5fb6fc73efa","tid":539052,"uid":24642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72e6bb165ab93e1f51ec2d0d217083d4698bca5e","tid":539052,"uid":28354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8150e3a6472b8ea67dc1128763aaf5fd3a776b63","tid":539052,"uid":51021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e958671e74c063df243342007e542de14d9dfe","tid":539052,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"輻射唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n顯影劑好似冇乜問題<br />\n個問題係有極少人會敏感, 導致生命危險, 所以要簽紙<br />\n你已經試過即係冇敏感, 再落都應該冇事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:16:43.000Z","msg":"顯影劑應該係radioactive <br />\n不過應該劑量好細 坐小幾次飛機都係返度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:19:09.000Z","msg":"同埋照咁睇應該4 5個月會decay曬"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:04:01.000Z","msg":"電腦掃瞄用嘅顯影劑係唔具放射性㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係講緊核子醫學同正電子掃瞄打嘅藥就係具放射性喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電腦掃瞄用嘅顯影劑多數係iodine嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你腎功能正常 個顯影劑就唔會對你有咩影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d08ca57492712767a32e9df7d4ef295b291edb","tid":539052,"uid":51021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c26554ecf684de887a15982464529189be15ff","tid":539052,"uid":67649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"CT 顯影劑唔係 radioactive 的。<br />\n<br />\nFrom US FDA<br />\n「A CT examination with an effective dose of 10 millisieverts (abbreviated mSv; 1 mSv = 1 mGy in the case of x-rays.) may be associated with an increase in the possibility of fatal cancer of approximately 1 chance in 2000. This increase in the possibility of a fatal cancer from radiation can be compared to the natural incidence of fatal cancer in the U.S. population, about 1 chance in 5 (equal to 400 chances in 2000). In other words, for any one person the risk of radiation-induced cancer is much smaller than the natural risk of cancer. If you combine the natural risk of a fatal cancer and the estimated risk from a 10 mSv CT scan, <span style=\"color: red;\">the total risk may increase from 400 chances in 2000 to 401 chances in 2000.</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fda.gov/Radiation-EmittingProducts/RadiationEmittingProductsandProcedures/MedicalImaging/MedicalX-Rays/ucm115329.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2FRadiation-EmittingProducts%2FRadiationEmittingProductsandProcedures%2FMedicalImaging%2FMedicalX-Rays%2Fucm115329.htm&d=ORNTrwOGgTfFwb0C8nnRxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6c5314f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fda.gov/Radiation-EmittingProducts/RadiationEmittingProductsandProcedures/MedicalImaging/MedicalX-Rays/ucm115329.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然照CT 係有輻射，不過劑量好少，會導致癌症嘅機會好低，<br />\n同埋醫生order 得嘅應該有佢嘅需要，所以唔洗擔心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"內文冇講顯影劑<br />\n不過佢入面話做一次得1mSv<br />\n放射性職業全年max 20mSv 咁睇既話 照幾次應該冇乜事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/182800_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F182800_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=23b3c818&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0c6db964c756b83c59f87eb5d4901120bde3f3e","tid":539052,"uid":101237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:05:40.000Z","msg":"好謝咁多位巴絲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114bf18c0bfa206a19fc4207d170cfac78fb5c01","tid":539052,"uid":101237,"like":0,"d